{"tid":1934394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日鄭松泰喺立法會大會爆黑警對手足濫用酷刑","createTime":"2020-03-20T02:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T08:26:52.000Z","uid":264325,"like":82,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"41dd470adbf2d177bdfe33f7c8101b3842834367","tid":1934394,"uid":264325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:16:59.000Z","msg":"利申唔鍾意熱狗 但係今日松泰爆咗一單好嚴重嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n話說尋日立法會大會 朱凱迪用議事規則40(1)提出中止待續 去到松泰發言嗰陣 佢喺大埔區議員黃兆健口中得知 當佢去荔枝角公務探訪探手足監嘅時候 嗰位手足喺<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>被捕前冇任何傷痕</strong></span> 但係當佢<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">送到青衣狗屋之後  俾狗打佢嘅腹部同肋骨 之後因為拒絕提供手機密碼 就被蒙面 頭部被連續拳打腳踢5分鐘</span></span></strong> 手足要求驗傷 但係班狗就俾杯水佢 叫佢唔好報警 去到醫院6日 冇沖過涼 冇換過基本衣物 律師同屋企人完全唔知道佢受到黑警酷刑 而醫生診斷後 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢嘅眼有三成視力冇辦法清楚睇到嘢 頭部有後遺症</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢單嘢其他傳媒冇報導過 一定要煲大佢！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d126f2dd95b4e7d02031bbe78ae6842ed92b177e","tid":1934394,"uid":136661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13caa3f12ac751d33aa3aa4ab06f2f383b4d0814","tid":1934394,"uid":331551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15e2bd6928b473e203235955f844c0bab0286627","tid":1934394,"uid":286832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"796f8cbcb5aa15786d27efc09913c27e142f5541","tid":1934394,"uid":276548,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T02:26:24.000Z","msg":"選舉近了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚再比呢班共諜呃呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VmvItk-RT3I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu